ZH: 我们乘坐了游船搭了一次风景之旅。
EN: We took a cruise to go on a scenic trip.

ZH: 他每天搭公交车上班。
EN: He takes the bus to work every day.

ZH: 我们要搭火车去旅行。
EN: We are going to travel by train.

ZH: 她一直想搭飞机去国外看望家人。
EN: She always wants to take a plane to visit her family abroad.

ZH: 老师让我去搭那个梯子。
EN: The teacher asked me to go and climb that ladder.

ZH: 我们需要搭一个脚手架来修理房顶。
EN: We need to set up scaffolding to repair the roof.

ZH: 他喜欢搭木筏在湖上划船。
EN: He enjoys using a wooden raft to row on the lake.

ZH: 我们决定搭顶篷帐篷露营。
EN: We decided to set up a tent to go camping.

ZH: 他和朋友们搭个棚在院子里开派对。
EN: He and his friends built a tent in the backyard to have a party.

ZH: 请在建筑上搭一个脚手架。
EN: Please construct a scaffolding for the building.

ZH: 我们需要搭个舞台供演员们表演。
EN: We need to set up a stage for the actors to perform.

ZH: 妈妈请你搭个凳子帮我够到眼镜。
EN: Mom, can you get me a stool to help me reach my glasses?

ZH: 在这片广场上搭个摊位去卖东西。
EN: Let's set up a stall on this square to sell things.

ZH: 他勇敢地搭上了过山车。
EN: He bravely got on the roller coaster.

ZH: 请搭个手梯帮我换灯泡。
EN: Please set up a step ladder for me to change the light bulb.

ZH: 他们正在搭桥修理这条道路。
EN: They are building a bridge to repair this road.

ZH: 我们可以去搭个帐篷露营。
EN: We can go and pitch a tent to go camping.

ZH: 请把梯子搭在墙边。
EN: Please lean the ladder against the wall.

ZH: 我们需要搭个脚手架来装修房子。
EN: We need to set up scaffolding to renovate the house.

ZH: 我会教你搭帐篷。
EN: I will teach you how to pitch a tent.
